Intelligent & Autonomous

Advanced sensors and AI-powered soiling detection allow Solaris V3 to autonomously navigate diverse solar panel layouts, identify dust levels, and adapt its cleaning process for optimal results.

Advanced Cleaning & Safety

Gentle microfiber helical brush ensures panel integrity, while obstacle detection, anti-fall protection, and weather adaptability guarantee safe operation in all conditions.

Eco-Friendly & Self-Sustaining

Integrated flexible solar panels power Solaris V3, making it a sustainable, energy-independent solution for solar panel maintenance.

Real-Time Monitoring & Insights

Remotely monitor, schedule, and track performance. Collect valuable data on panel conditions to support proactive maintenance and maximize efficiency.
